msgstr "2D场景的相机节点。"

#: ../../docs/classes/class_camera2d.rst:17
msgid "Description"
msgstr "说明"

#: ../../docs/classes/class_camera2d.rst:19
msgid ""
"Camera node for 2D scenes. It forces the screen (current layer) to scroll"
" following this node. This makes it easier (and faster) to program "
"scrollable scenes than manually changing the position of :ref:`CanvasItem"
" <class_CanvasItem>`-based nodes."
msgstr ""
"2D场景的相机节点。它强制屏幕（当前层）在此节点之后滚动。与手动更改基于 :ref:`CanvasItem <class_CanvasItem>`"
" 的节点的位置相比，这使得对可滚动场景进行编程更加容易（并且速度更快）。"

#: ../../docs/classes/class_camera2d.rst:21
msgid ""
"This node is intended to be a simple helper to get things going quickly "
"and it may happen that more functionality is desired to change how the "
"camera works. To make your own custom camera node, simply inherit from "
":ref:`Node2D <class_Node2D>` and change the transform of the canvas by "
"calling get_viewport().set_canvas_transform(m) in :ref:`Viewport "
"<class_Viewport>`."
msgstr ""
"该节点旨在成为使事情快速进行的简单助手器，并且可能会需要更多功能来更改相机的工作方式。要创建自己的自定义相机节点，只需继承 "
":ref:`Node2D <class_Node2D>`，并通过调用 :ref:`Viewport <class_Viewport>` 中的 "
"``get_viewport().set_canvas_transform(m)`` 即可更改画布的变换。"

